COMMITTEE AMENDMENT

COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “ ” to H.P. 347, L.D. 528
1 Amend the bill by relettering or renumbering any nonconsecutive Part letter or section
2 number to read consecutively.
3 SUMMARY
44 This amendment explicitly adds to the bill licensed veterinary technicians under the
55 indirect supervision of a licensed veterinarian to those persons authorized to administer
66 rabies vaccinations.
